Breaking Bad is one of those TV series that is so good that you want to keep seeing more and more episodes each day. Also the characters are all great Walter White, Jesse, Hank, Gustavo, Mike, Saul even Skyler who is being portrayed as the annoying character of the show it works because there's an actual good script behind the show and you can easily see that from just the first 5 minutes of the 1st episode. You have great characters, actors, direction and at this point iconic lines like 'Say my Name' or 'I'm the One who Knocks' or even iconic deaths like the head on top of the turtle and Gustavo's half Terminator death. Breaking Bad is just Awesometacular!!!